Sure Shamu, since its fixed now I guess no harm.<br>
<br>
Here's what happened:  There was a mob you'd kill, and about eight smaller mobs would spawn.  When you'd loot them, you would read &quot;You recieve 154328954 gold and 667346724 silver as your split.&quot;  I wish I'd logged it!<br>
<br>
That many digits, I shit you not.  Guys, 10-20K per fish?  Hahaha.  Thats Funny.  No friends and neighbors, try 10-20MILLION.<br>
<br>
It was not a legit drop... it would crash you to charselect screen.  There was more you had to do to get TO your new money, because that insane amount of coin crashed the game...  Anyways its all fixed, and I was given a warning for explotation.  Those who tried to sell dirty plat online?  I would imagine they might get more than a warning.   <br>
<br>
GM contacted me about 48 hours later, and asked if I cared to explain.  I sang like a canary, &quot;I found an exploit, and didn't report it.  I thought about it, but ultimately did not.&quot;  No names though, not that I had any.<br>
